The platform agent is the one in charge of selecting on behalf of the end user which plug-ins or services to use. For
that it takes into account the costs associated to using them and the relation with its benefits.

Many parts of the platforms are based on third party components which comes with a use license which is not free. As
there are more than one implementation available someone has to choose which one to use.

The platform agent has the intelligence enough to choose what to use and what to avoid.